org.eclipse.xtext.xbase.lib

Annotation Type ReassignFirstArgument


  • @Beta
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
@Documented
@GwtCompatible
public @interface ReassignFirstArgument
    The annotated function assigns the returned value to the first argument. That is, it is required that the first argument is a reference to an assignable variable or field.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Anton Kosyakov - Initial contribution and API
